Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.79,0:01:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.39,0:01:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.33,0:01:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.07,0:02:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.55,0:02:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#15  ちぃ，什麼都不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.76,0:03:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚沒睡好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.59,0:03:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保跟清水老師\N竟然是那種關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.53,0:03:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羨慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保你太令人羨慕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.83,0:03:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師不是結婚了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保也不可能是她老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和有夫之婦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是有夫之婦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜夜春宵的有夫之婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早不要看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.57,0:03:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有夫之婦指的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟男人結了婚的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.18,0:03:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.48,0:04:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是做早操的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先從手部運動開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.60,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼絲茉茉會在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.67,0:04:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.31,0:04:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我保管，拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.38,0:04:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.15,0:04:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人果然很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的，搞什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘後要出門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.36,0:04:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是做這種事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.53,0:04:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.35,0:05:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師還沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有時會早到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她從來沒遲到過的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.05,0:05:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師到最後還是沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保那傢伙也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個到底在搞什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.81,0:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.91,0:05:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我要這個跟這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.78,0:05:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過新保那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛又要託我保管絲茉茉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.19,0:05:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，手，手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.40,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.81,0:06:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.94,0:06:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要改變時間嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為棒球比賽轉播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.12,0:06:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預定錄影的節目\N被延後三十分鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼大聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我打工的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.56,0:06:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要改變設定時間嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之回背包裡面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，那台電腦是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.08,0:06:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保不知道什麼時候\N偷放到我的背包裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要我幫他保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.28,0:06:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來，幹嘛要我保管呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既不會成為包袱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會妨礙到他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但方便、漂亮\N還什麼都會替你做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.43,0:07:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦真的有很多好處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.47,0:07:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該對裕美發牢騷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.48,0:07:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管牢騷還是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都全年無休，照單全收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，裕美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是一團糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是新保那傢伙害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請趕快接聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請趕快接聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再響五聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.96,0:07:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會轉到答錄機模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.14,0:07:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個聲音，你是新保對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在搞什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟老師私奔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.39,0:07:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要插在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是把這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出來，快出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.33,0:08:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出來，快出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.87,0:08:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這邊才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.91,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…那裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，自己接好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.45,0:08:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師我很高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.65,0:08:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯什麼嗯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.69,0:08:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私奔是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.56,0:08:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同我說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟清水老師現在私奔中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.06,0:08:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.03,0:08:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛跟補習班老師私奔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.47,0:08:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候\N跟她開始交往的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經快半年了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是\N剛到補習班上課的時候嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在我不注意時跟老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.21,0:08:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢瞞著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.18,0:09:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我說了也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼重要的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這台電視不但是舊型  又便宜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.56,0:09:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接的方法一定也不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒時間煩惱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在必須…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.74,0:09:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，我去稔家裡一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.74,0:09:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要乖乖看家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是“私奔”？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是好事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是壞事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.12,0:09:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道\N該怎麼回答才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.63,0:09:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.90,0:09:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.00,0:09:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.28,0:10:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,補習班學生竟然跟老師私奔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底在想什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保這個大混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和少爺來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼晚了，發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.50,0:10:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去準備本須和少爺的茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真誇張的出場方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.54,0:10:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託將她接到有畫面的電話線上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指超高速通信線路嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.91,0:10:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.81,0:10:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟誰通電話呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞私奔的混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經接上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.63,0:11:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫面會出現在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.94,0:11:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.54,0:11:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上會出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.17,0:11:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，你在國分寺家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.04,0:11:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續剛剛的話題，新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要瞞著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.68,0:11:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先跟你說也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是把你當作朋友喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.06,0:11:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也當你是朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此，為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.63,0:11:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為多香子不同意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.57,0:11:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道多香子已經結婚了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師告訴我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次在我那邊過夜的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚之後馬上就迷上電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.28,0:11:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫妻間的談話\N變得都是電腦的話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.62,0:11:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.82,0:11:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子以為他只是\N剛買了電腦高興過頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.55,0:11:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以也沒在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.46,0:11:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一段時間之後\N她丈夫就只跟電腦說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管多香子在不在他身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只跟電腦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.93,0:12:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對電腦不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概想不通吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近這種人一直在增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得電腦比較可愛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.61,0:12:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和人類比起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.34,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟電腦在一起比較快樂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.81,0:12:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些話就是指這件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離補習班不遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個小公園對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是剛到補習班的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.86,0:12:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某天傍晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.03,0:12:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我經過那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.37,0:12:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候還是叫她清水老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時老師她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在鞦韆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為她只是童心大發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想玩玩鞦韆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.05,0:12:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有叫她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我吃完晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.99,0:13:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經很晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.19,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻還在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.30,0:13:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.53,0:13:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這裡做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為門鎖上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳忘了帶鑰匙了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙我是有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.33,0:13:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是上了門鍊，打不開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門鍊是指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有人在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.34,0:13:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.59,0:14:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們吵架了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵架啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.39,0:14:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很久沒有吵架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連話都說不上兩句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.00,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好罵他幾句不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她搖了搖頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.24,0:14:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了門鍊就表示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.21,0:14:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公忘了我會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.58,0:14:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不在家都沒影響了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.83,0:14:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得怎樣都無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.77,0:15:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得怎樣都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明在說這麼傷心的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻沒有哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.78,0:15:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她其實很想哭出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.02,0:15:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是拼命在忍耐罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.79,0:15:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想至少讓她在遇到\N不愉快或傷心的事時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠哭個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我迷上她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後我就窮追不捨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.37,0:16:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是補習班學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是補習班老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.84,0:16:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且已經結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我說了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.18,0:16:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直追，一直追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.32,0:16:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就變成了今天這個局面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此，為什麼要私奔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.73,0:16:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道只剩這個方法了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們這個年紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.70,0:16:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是小鬼而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.06,0:16:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許就如同你所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是我的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.74,0:16:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得不相信男性的人類了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.05,0:16:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她認為就算一開始說喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦出現像電腦那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會完全改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像從沒喜歡過一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.69,0:17:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她說過我是不一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不管說幾次她還是不信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次多香子到本須和房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本打算兩人好好談談的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.64,0:17:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談談關於我們的將來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.34,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過事到臨頭\N她好像還是害怕了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.25,0:17:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人的心還真是難懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.96,0:17:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓她跑掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定私奔到深山的溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.50,0:17:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣濕答答的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是旅行而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩恩愛愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說，這算是私奔啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.80,0:17:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.97,0:17:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在多香子點頭之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.81,0:17:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點頭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我再婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.48,0:17:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.51,0:17:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚，再婚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉再幫我保管一段時間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫你保管當然沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.86,0:18:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟誰在通電話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟本須和啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比平常性感好幾倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜囉，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.27,0:18:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會再跟你聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.27,0:18:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.34,0:18:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.58,0:18:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再有什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.71,0:18:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.01,0:18:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.61,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我這種重考生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫不了你太大的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過或許我可以幫上什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.82,0:18:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.86,0:18:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.26,0:18:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，新保這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.18,0:18:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.81,0:19:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為人太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.75,0:19:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果只能當個商量的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，還是在室男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.62,0:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是到本須和房間去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我找了一個晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.33,0:19:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.63,0:19:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我鬧得很凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄得他很疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好像很睏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎是無意識狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我試著問了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經結婚的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能喜歡上別人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.53,0:19:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上一個人，是無法抗拒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對自己的另一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.77,0:20:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喜歡上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有對自己都是痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在其中徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.41,0:20:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己覺得自在就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.32,0:20:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這麼對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.06,0:20:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然說得出這種大道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.59,0:20:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明還是在室男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過不知為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.90,0:20:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心裡像是放下一塊大石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.93,0:20:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己覺得自在就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.14,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到他這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.07,0:20:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺輕鬆多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了更輕鬆自在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.11,0:20:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要到我身邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.28,0:20:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒，就是表示快了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.45,0:20:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是無憂無慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.32,0:20:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.49,0:20:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都到這裡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.79,0:20:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還叫我新保啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼問題來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.50,0:21:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳猜猜\N我一直想要妳怎麼叫我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.94,0:21:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿弘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.84,0:21:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.75,0:21:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是個好人，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.56,0:21:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖是好人卻沒有女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.60,0:21:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷上電腦的丈夫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.74,0:21:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算讓女孩流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.68,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是覺得電腦比較好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.44,0:22:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.21,0:22:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.46,0:22:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.44,0:23:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷找尋著一閃即逝的藍色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.16,0:23:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.53,0:23:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後不再遺忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.63,0:23:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有多心痛         也要在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.35,0:23:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠         直到永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.50,0:23:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.03,0:23:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.36,0:23:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.17,0:23:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.17,0:23:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.00,0:23:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.90,0:23:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.54,0:23:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.54,0:23:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.40,0:23:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多加努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.71,0:23:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.47,0:23:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要更努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.07,0:23:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.81,0:23:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更更要努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.74,0:23:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.51,0:23:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.01,0:24:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
